1. Finalized list of business rules \
Identification:\
* Each student must have a unique student_ID\
* Each faculty Member must have a unique Faculty_ID\
* Each class must have a unique class_ID\
* Each classroom must have a unque Room_ID\
\
Student and enrollment:\
* A student may enroll in multiple classes\
* Each student is assigned exactly one academic advisor\
* A class may have muliple students\
* Each class has a max capacity\
* Attendance must be recorded for each student for the day, for each class\
* Grades are calculateed for each student, for each class, for each semester\
\
Faculty:\
* Each class is taught by exactly one faculty member\
* A faculty member may teach multiple classes\
* An advisor may advise multiple students\
\
Class and Classroom:\
* Each class must be assigned to exactly one classroom\
* Each classroom belongs to exactly one building\
* One class per classroom at one time\
* A building may contain multiple classrooms\
